      "text": [
        "652 - وَقَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «لَفَضْلُ اَلْوَقْتِ اَلْأَوَّلِ عَلَى اَلْأَخِيرِ خَيْرٌ لِلْمُؤْمِنِ مِنْ وُلْدِهِ وَ مَالِهِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.652 - Imam (as) said:\n\"The merit of performing (prayer) at the earliest time compared to the latest time is better for a believer than their children and wealth.\""
        ]
      }
    },
